{"tid":1905583,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"2020 香港警察濫權濫暴資料庫重整計劃 寫於重組前 (3月上旬)","createTime":"2020-03-01T10:56:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T07:00:45.000Z","uid":252591,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d77499d4e8163566e026c20c0bec085b8acc7064","tid":1905583,"uid":252591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:56:32.000Z","msg":"前言: 而家既網站係19年 7月中 構思 8月初開始做<br />\n跟隨運動一路做落去 當中有數之不盡既不足<br />\n直到而家 收埋左幾十 GB 既資料<br />\n加上好多人既報料  所以決定重制網站<br />\n<br />\n做呢個網站最辛苦除左付出好多時間同面對精神壓力<br />\n睇到咁多手足甚至普通人被黑狗恐襲既相同片先至係內心最難頂個一刻<br />\n所以請大家支持 <a href=\"http://www.hkcpgdb.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcpgdb.com&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGosbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=0b7e9dd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hkcpgdb.com</a> 以及其他手足 (包括前線 文宣 家長 國外手足例如我)<br />\n光復香港 時代革命 香港精神 永不言敗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n寫於重組前 (2020年 3月上旬)<br />\n<br />\n網址: <a href=\"http://www.hkcpgdb.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcpgdb.com&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGosbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=0b7e9dd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hkcpgdb.com</a><br />\nTG id: <a href=\"http://t.me/hkcpgdb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkcpgdb&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGosbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=dd9be716\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkcpgdb</a><br />\n報料 Email: hkcpgdb@protonmail.com<br />\n<br />\n請求任何方法支持，包括輕輕推一推個 Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Share 呢個 Post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以及提出建議及意見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2020 香港警察濫權濫暴資料庫重整計劃 寫於重組前 (3月上旬)<br />\n- 新增 Timeline 頁<br />\n- 新增 infographic  頁<br />\n- 新增黑狗臭名萬世專區<br />\n- 新增納粹軍政府反人類歷史記錄冊<br />\n- 新增神經失常智力有缺憾黑狗記錄冊<br />\n- 新增肢體失調事件黑狗記錄冊<br />\n​- 新增黑狗失職記錄冊<br />\n- 新增重大事記錄冊<br />\n- 運動同路人連結專頁<br />\n- 辱民黑警專區 (以回應要求辱狗罪之訴求)<br />\n- (無)可疑被自殺記錄冊<br />\n- 加入亞州第一黑警隊招募文宣記錄冊"},{"pid":"6a3d121a197b2c71893bb11dc86d0bb9b3c0feff","tid":1905583,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:59:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d12b3b7cb10b6959ca28a6bbe1aea8837641bcfd","tid":1905583,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:00:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"624fd4bca4a43391e454ef5db6cbfcb12b65aaf1","tid":1905583,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:00:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9c866e6e2c606202ea7d3a820e37164d7af4cf1","tid":1905583,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:00:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb8816c637049a5496b87cce50ae16e6026c1406","tid":1905583,"uid":252591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a3d121a197b2c71893bb11dc86d0bb9b3c0feff","tid":1905583,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:59:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:01:15.000Z","msg":"多謝你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b01b2030d5012e1d2696991e1dbe9a999478c0","tid":1905583,"uid":39503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:02:33.000Z","msg":"推，辛苦手足"},{"pid":"e33794396f0902f318162af2170f1e57e9a74d94","tid":1905583,"uid":65962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:05:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cee7e8abf5eaabecbaaa2130562006e4aeac17c","tid":1905583,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:06:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同場加映 <a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https